  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Privacy Policy – Any Tasker

Last Updated: 11 December 2025

Welcome to Any Tasker.
Your privacy is very important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our website and tools.

1. Information We Collect

We do not collect any personally identifiable information from users.

However, depending on the tools you use, the website may temporarily handle the following data:

a. Uploaded Images / Files

When you use tools like Image Converter, Photo to Text, or any other upload-based tools, your files are processed locally in your browser.

We do not store, save, or send your images/files to any server.

b. Non-personal Data

We may collect non-personal information such as:

Browser type

Device type

Pages visited

Time spent on the site

This is used only for improving website performance.

2. How We Use the Information

We use collected data ONLY for:

Running website features

Improving tool performance

Fixing bugs and errors

Enhancing user experience

We never sell, share, or trade your data with any third party.

3. Cookies

Our website may use basic cookies for:

Website performance

Tool functionality

We do not use cookies to track personal information.

4. Third-Party Services

Our site may use:

GitHub Pages (for hosting)

Google Fonts or CDN libraries

These services may collect non-personal analytics data according to their own privacy policies.

We do not control how third-party services collect or use such data.

5. Data Security

Your files are processed client-side (inside your browser).

We do not store any user files on any server.

We follow standard security practices to keep the site safe.

6. Links to Other Websites

Our website may contain external links.
We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those websites.

7. Children’s Privacy

Our tools are suitable for all ages.
We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Changes will be posted on this page with the updated date.

9. Contact Us

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
Email: anytasker1998@gmail.com
 (आप अपने हिसाब से बदल सकते हैं).</p>
